import '../CSS/Index.css'
// import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
// import PalmSugar from '../img/ice coffee palm sugar.png'
// import GreenTea from '../img/ice coffee green tea.png'
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
import {Stack } from 'react-bootstrap'

const LetsOrder = () => {
    return(
        <>
        
          
            <Stack>
            <Container>
            <Row md={4} >
                <Col>
                <Card style={{ width: '15rem' }}>
                <Card.Img variant="top" src={require ('../img/ice coffee palm sugar.png')} />
                <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>Ice Coffee Palm Sugar</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                    Rp.27.000
                    </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
                </Card>
                </Col>

                <Col >
                <Card style={{ width: '15rem' }}>
                <Card.Img variant="top" src= {require ('../img/ice coffee green tea.png')} />
                <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>Ice Coffee Green tea</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                    Rp. 31.000
                    </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
                </Card>
                </Col>

                <Col>
                <Card style={{ width: '15rem' }}>
                <Card.Img variant="top" src={require ('../img/hanami latte.png')} />
                <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>Hanami Latte</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                    Rp.29.000
                    </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
                </Card>
                </Col>


                <Col>
                <Card style={{ width: '15rem' }}>
                <Card.Img variant="top" src={require ('../img/clepon cofee.png')} />
                <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>Clepon Coffee</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                    Rp. 28.000
                    </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
                </Card>
                </Col>
            </Row>
            </Container>
            </Stack>
            



            
        
        </>
    )
}

export default LetsOrder
